courseName: Data Science and Artificial Intelligence (Conversion Programme) MSc
facultyName: School of Electronic Engineering and Computer Science
description: The MSc Data Science and Artificial Intelligence is a conversion master’s designed for motivated students who have a good first degree in a subject other than Computer Science, who wish to develop the knowledge and skills to gain employment in the Data Science and Artificial Intelligence industry.
